data.description: New Construction lakefront custom home to be completed May 1 2022, features impact windows and doors, oversized garage w storage & paver circular driveway leading to large front porch w eye catching stone work & wood tongue & grove custom ceilings. Marvel at the peaceful and spectacular stunning long Lake views from the open concept living space w designer kitchen, solid wood cabinets, upgraded matching quartz countertops, high end appliances, walk in pantry & butler's pantry. Great room features state of the art electric  fireplace & high end wood grain porcelain tile throughout. This is an estate you will be proud to own and the quality of material and workmanship used will keep you happy and worry free for many years to come.
